      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy testing with manufactured solutions and documented convergence rates for all governing equations used in the hemolysis model.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not for the scalar hemolysis transport equation. Convergence rates documented only for velocity fields. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
