      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent on at least three systematically refined meshes; grid convergence index reported for hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted; however, GCI was reported only for pressure drop, not for the hemolysis index QoI. Discretization error on the primary QoI remains unquantified. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
