      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions are partially documented; inlet flow waveform uncertainty is not reported, and the blood analog viscosity deviates by up to 12% from clinical blood at high shear rates. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
