      "rationale": "No formal user qualification records or execution checklists are available for the VAD simulation campaign. Independent review of model setup was not performed. Flagged as epistemic gap; achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection with documented justification for applicability to VAD flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected without documented comparison to alternative models for the transitional flow regime present in VAD impeller passages. Hemolysis constitutive model selection is not justified for high-shear VAD conditions. Flagged as critical epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
