      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo propagation completed with documented convergence of output statistics.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated for inlet boundary conditions and viscosity, but parameter distributions for wall roughness, impeller clearance tolerances, and hemolysis model coefficients were not characterized. UQ coverage is insufficient for MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
