    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted as a complete documentation artifact for regulatory submission purposes. The decision outcome reflects acceptance of the package structure and completeness of the 13-factor assessment record. The underlying simulation evidence is not accepted for device clearance; all seven assessed factors fall below required levels, and six factors are flagged as unassessed epistemic gaps. This package is forwarded to the regulatory authority with the explicit finding that the CFD model does not meet MRL 5 credibility requirements for Class III VAD hemolysis prediction.",
